targets.expr: 100 * avg(gitlab_database_rows{query_name="container_repositories_import_done", environment="${environment}", shard="default", type="patroni"}) / (avg(gitlab_database_rows{query_name="container_repositories_migration_pending", environment="${environment}", shard="default", type="patroni"}) + avg(gitlab_database_rows{query_name="container_repositories_import_done", environment="${environment}", shard="default", type="patroni"}))

panels.description: Estimated days to completion of free tier migration. Based on the hourly estimated import rate.

targets.expr:
(
    avg(gitlab_database_rows{query_name="container_repositories_migration_pending", environment="gprd", shard="default", type="patroni"}) 
    / 
    avg(increase(gitlab_database_rows{query_name="container_repositories_import_done", environment="gprd", shard="default", type="patroni"}[1h]))
) / 24

panels.title: Days to completion
